=====================
gnome-themes-standard 
=====================

This package contains various components of the default GNOME 3 theme.

src/: the Adwaita GTK+ 3 theming engine

themes/Adwaita/
  backgrounds/: the default GNOME 3 wallpaper
  cursors/: the default GNOME 3 cursor theme
  gtk-2.0/: the default GNOME 3 theme for GTK+ 2 applications
  gtk-3.0/: the default GNOME 3 theme for GTK+ 3 applications
  metacity-1/: the default GNOME 3 window manager theme

themes/HighContrast/: the default HighContrast GNOME 3 theme for GTK+ 2 and
                      GTK+ 3 applications

themes/HighContrastInverse: the default HighContrastInverse GNOME 3 theme for
                            GTK+ 2 and GTK+ 3 applications

themes/LowContrast/: a low contrast variation of the default GNOME 3 theme
                     for GTK+ 2 and GTK+ 3 applications

Installation
============

See the 'INSTALL' file for installation instructions. You will need an
up-to-date GTK+ 3 development environment to build the package.

How to report bugs
==================

Bugs should be reported to the GNOME Bugzilla [1], choosing the 
"gnome-themes-standard" product.

[1] https://bugzilla.gnome.org
